in-inducing agents.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/57427/', '', 'Meloxicam', 'Lidocaine, Zinc sulfate, Diltiazem, Tetracaine, Zinc acetate, Fluocinolone acetonide, Hydrocortisone, Fluocinonide, Zinc chloride, Procaine, Prednisolone, More', 1767369485);
